      • onEnterUnsubscribed

        public void onEnterUnsubscribed(UnsubscribeRequest request,
                                UnsubscribeReply reply)
        Description copied from interface: SubscriptionListener
        Called when a subscription enters the unsubscribed state. This is the initial state for the subscription lifecycle.

        A subscription enters this state in the following situations:

        • The subscription was created and initialized with the unsubscribed state
        • The connection is dropped
        • RtmClient.removeSubscription() method is called
        Specified by:
        onEnterUnsubscribed in interface SubscriptionListener
        Parameters:
        request - unsubscribe request PDU
        reply - unsubscribe response PDU
